{
  "name": "Tab",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Chart/Chart .htm#Chart.Chart\">Chart</a></strong> 对象或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.Worksheet\">Worksheet</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Chart/Chart .htm#Chart.Tab\">Tab</a></strong> 属性可返回一个 <strong>Tab</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>一旦返回了 <strong>Tab</strong> 对象，您就可以使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Tab/Tab .htm#Tab.ColorIndex\">ColorIndex</a></strong> 属性来确定图表或工作表标签的设置。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为ET判断第一个工作表的标签的颜色索引是否设置为无，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Determine if color index of 1st tab is set to none.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexNone) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The color index is set to none for the first worksheet tab.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The color index for the tab of the first worksheet is not set none.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 选项卡的颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tab = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>\n    tab.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n    tab.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表图表或工作表中的标签。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Color",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>对象</th>\n<th>对应颜色</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>Border</strong></td>\n<td>边框的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Borders</strong></td>\n<td>一个区域的所有四条边的颜色。如果四边不是同一种颜色，则 <strong>Color</strong> 返回的是 0（零）。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Font</strong></td>\n<td>字体的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interior</strong></td>\n<td>单元格底纹的颜色或图形对象的填充颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Tab</strong></td>\n<td>选项卡的颜色。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置对象的主要颜色，如注释部分中的表格所示。使用 <strong>RGB</strong> 函数可创建颜色值。<strong>Variant</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置图表工作表 Chart1 选项卡的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>)\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 选项卡的颜色设置为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorIndex",
      "summary": "<p>返回 <strong>Tab</strong> 对象后，可以使用 <strong>ColorIndex</strong> 属性来确定图表或工作表的选项卡设置。</p>\n<p>颜色可指定为当前调色板中颜色的索引值 1 到 56，也可指定为下列 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlColorIndex 枚举.html\">XlColorIndex</a></strong> 常量之一：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexNone</strong></li>\n<li><strong>xlColorIndexAutomatic</strong></li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Variant</strong> 值，它代表指定的工作表或图表选项卡的颜色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为ET判断第一个工作表的标签的颜色索引是否设置为无，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Determine if color index of 1st tab is set to none.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == xlColorIndexNone) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The color index is set to none for the first worksheet tab.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The color index for the tab of the first worksheet is not set none.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 选项卡的颜色设置为黄色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlColorIndex",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ThemeColor",
      "summary": "<p>如果对象当前未应用主题颜色，试图访问其主题颜色则会引起无效请求运行时错误。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置已应用的配色方案中的主题颜色，该配色方案与指定对象相关联。可读/写 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlThemeColor 枚举.html\">XlThemeColor</a></strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 选项卡的主题颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent4\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 选项卡的主题颜色是否为xlThemeColorAccent1。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> == xlThemeColorAccent1)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlThemeColor",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TintAndShade",
      "summary": "<p>可以为 <strong>TintAndShade</strong> 属性输入 -1（最暗）到 1（最亮）之间的数字，零 (0) 为中间值。</p>\n<p>建议不要尝试将此属性设置为小于 -1 或大于 1 的值。ET 将在内部将该值更正为属于有效值范围内的某个值。此属性用于主题颜色和非主题颜色。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>Single</strong>，使颜色变深或变浅。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 选项卡的颜色亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置图表工作表 Chart1 选项卡的颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>)\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Tab</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = -<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.2</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}